<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عِكْرِمَةُ:</span> <span class="c1">" هَيْتَ لَكَ بِالحَوْرَانِيَّةِ: هَلُمَّ "</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ جُبَيْرٍ:</span> <span class="c2">«تَعَالَهْ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>